                "Agatha Pricilla, Indy Barends, Lutesha, Salvita Decorte \n" +
                "Zulfa Maharani, Widi Mulia, Baskara Mahendra - Jojo\n" +
                "Baim Wong, Kevin Ardilova, Oka Antara, Brandon Salim\n" +
                "Edward Suhadi, Darius Sinathrya,Joseph Kara - Kepala sekolah\n",
        "2019",
        ),
)
